data.description: Welcome home to your new affordable 55+ community in Belleview called Tropicana Village. This 3 bedroom 2 bath home features a workshop/storage area. 5 years ago home was updated to include fresh paint, new carpet and new vinyl wood grain flooring. Enjoy the gorgeous Florida mornings with a cup of coffee on your screen in lanai. Roof is 2016 with workshop/storage. Best part the HOA fees are only $70 month and includes water and trash with access to the community pool and club house.  SELLER WILL PROVIDE $2,000 CREDIT TOWARDS CLOSING COSTS & PREPAIDS.  Home is on Supra - please note that key is for bottom lock only.   Don’t miss out on this great opportunity!
